Package: BayesProj
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Projection of Demographic Indicators
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "John",
             family = "Bryant",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "john@bayesiandemography.com"),
      person(given = "Junni",
             family = "Zhang",
             role = "aut",
             email = "junnizhang@163.com"))
Description: Bayesian projection of demographic indicators.
    The projections are based on time series models and,
    optionally, expert judgement. Expert judgements are specified
    through 'benchmarks' on future values. Estimation of the
    time series models is done internally via TMB.
